text: Ahsan Habib Lincoln is a Jatiya Party (Ershad) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Kushtia-2. ==Career== Lincoln was elected to parliament from Kushtia-2 as a Jatiya Party candidate in 1988. He is a politician of the Jatiya Party (Kazi Zafar) fraction. ==References== Category:Jatiya Party politicians Category:Living people Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
